snippet.title: Life On A Pizza - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
You are no longer the eater; you are the eaten. Play as toppings trying to survive on a pizza from the hungry monstrous Jaw biting its way to you and the ants pushing you to your delicious death. Customize the pizza’s color and shape, pick a game mode and your favourite topping, then hop in this hysterical party or solo game.


Music Used:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yfCgbdIHm2A
